Zulu: Ekuqaleni kwempi yahamba kakhulu ngaphezu kolwandle, kodwa njengoba ireda yaqala ukukhula nokucacisa okwengeziwe, imikhumbi yangaphansi komhlaba yaphoqelelwa ukuba ihambe ngaphansi kwamanzi ukuze ingabonwa. English: In the beginning of the war they mostly travelled on top of the sea, but as radar began developing and becoming more accurate the submarines were forced to go under water to avoid being seen. Zulu: Amahlathi awagcini nje ngokuba amaxhaphozi anemihlume — ahlanganisa ezinye zezindawo zokugcina ezisele zamahlathi anamandla ake ahlanganisa ithafa lase-Gangetic.
